parameters: Kyle: I want to face the final battle as well.
Kyle: I want to walk the same path as you all.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I'm so happy. Having you come... there's no stronger ally than
you.

Becky: Kyle-san... despite your strong opposition to fighting Lucia...
if you're with us, maybe a miracle will happen.

Kyle: Luuna, the matter with Mao and Mei... we also bear
responsibility.

Kyle: It's my fault that you're heading into a fight without any
chance of winning, with no strategy left.

Kyle: My subordinates couldn't save Mao and Mei from the generals of
Valentina.
Kyle: I'm truly sorry. For such cruelty...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Kyle-san, please don't blame yourself anymore.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Kyle-san, let's go together. To the final battle...
